So the point isn't to spice up

00:26:03.386 --> 00:26:04.806 A:middle
your copy, right?

00:26:05.236 --> 00:26:07.516 A:middle
The point is that spicy copy in

00:26:07.516 --> 00:26:08.966 A:middle
the right context feels

00:26:08.966 --> 00:26:09.666 A:middle
memorable.

00:26:12.356 --> 00:26:14.826 A:middle
And it must be said that the

00:26:14.826 --> 00:26:16.196 A:middle
personality of Carrot is

00:26:16.196 --> 00:26:17.666 A:middle
probably not for everyone.

00:26:18.416 --> 00:26:20.496 A:middle
And I talked with Brian he

00:26:20.496 --> 00:26:21.636 A:middle
