00:26:31.846 --> 00:26:33.366 A:middle
forecast after they download the

00:26:33.366 --> 00:26:33.636 A:middle
app.

00:26:33.776 --> 00:26:37.026 A:middle
Like, you know, how dare he

00:26:37.026 --> 00:26:39.526 A:middle
insult meteorologists like this?

00:26:40.986 --> 00:26:42.976 A:middle
So he offers an olive branch --

00:26:43.516 --> 00:26:45.546 A:middle
[ Laughter ]

00:26:46.046 --> 00:26:48.166 A:middle
To these disgruntled souls.

00:26:48.766 --> 00:26:50.636 A:middle
