00:26:50.636 --> 00:26:52.096 A:middle
from the default, which as you

00:26:52.196 --> 00:26:53.496 A:middle
saw was Homicidal.

00:26:53.716 --> 00:26:56.196 A:middle
You could go the left for less

00:26:56.196 --> 00:26:58.116 A:middle
